narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I only took this course because I had to, and though its not unbearable I certainly wouldn't recommend it to those following a casual interest in math--lectures were often boring and there are just so many better courses out there.
I would definitely recommend this course!
Yes its a great course but i recommend a background in math
This course was informative and very enjoyable. I absolutely recommend this course to my fellow students!
I would recommend it if you want a QR credit done and if you've taken calculus. If you haven't, the class will be difficult.
I would recommend this class to people who need it for a requirement or like math
Math 112 is a good class to take if you need the review or haven't taken calculus before. If they need calculus I would recommend this class to them.
